    All Classes and Interfaces

    Class
    Description
    Applicant
    Represents an applicant for BTO housing projects.
    Application
    Represents an application for a BTO flat.
    ApplicationStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of a BTO application.
    Enquiry
    Represents an enquiry about a BTO project.
    FlatType
    Represents the types of flats available in BTO projects.
    HDBManager
    Represents an HDB Manager who can create and manage BTO projects.
    HDBOfficer
    Represents an HDB Officer who can handle BTO projects.
    Project
    Represents a BTO housing project managed by HDB.
    Receipt
    Represents a receipt for a successful BTO flat booking.
    Registration
    Represents a registration request by an HDB Officer for a project.
    RegistrationStatus
    Represents the possible statuses of an HDB Officer's registration for a project.
    Report
    Represents a report generated by an HDB Manager.
    User
    Abstract base class for all users in the HDB system.
